msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr ""

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Deployment Mode | Total NPUs | Weight Version | Key Considerations |\n"
"| -------- | --------------- | ---------- | -------------- | ------------------ |\n"
"| Long context | Single-node online serving | 2 or more NPUs | W8A8 | Use larger `--max-model-len` and reserve enough KV cache. Lower `--max-num-seqs` if OOM occurs. |\n"
"| High throughput | Single-node online serving | 8 or more NPUs | W8A8 | Increase local DP groups within one node and tune `--max-num-batched-tokens`. |\n"
"| Low latency | Single-node online serving | 2 or more NPUs | W8A8 | Use smaller `--max-num-batched-tokens`, full decode ACLGraph, and disable speculative decoding by default. |"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Node Role | NPUs | TP | DP | Max Num Seqs | Max Model Len | Max Num Batched Tokens | Prefix Cache | Main Optimizations |\n"
"| -------- | --------- | ---- | -- | -- | ------------ | ------------- | ---------------------- | ------------ | ------------------ |\n"
"| Long context | Single node | 2 or more | 2 | 1 | 128 | 262144 | 16384 | On | FullGraph, FlashComm1, shared expert overlap, CPU binding |\n"
"| High throughput | Single node | 8 or more | 2 | 4 or more | 32 per DP | 65536 | 8192 | On | FullGraph, FlashComm1, async scheduling, shared expert overlap |\n"
"| Low latency | Single node | 2 or more | 2 | 1 | Tune by concurrency | 32768 or 65536 | 1024 to 4096 | Workload dependent | FullGraph, CPU binding, speculative decoding disabled |"
msgstr ""

msgid "### 9.2 Tuning Guidelines"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"1. Use single-node deployment. If more throughput is required, increase local DP groups within the same node.\n"
"2. Choose the maximum context length with `--max-model-len`. Long context increases KV cache usage, so reduce `--max-num-seqs` or `--gpu-memory-utilization` if OOM occurs.\n"
"3. Tune `--max-num-batched-tokens`. Larger values usually improve prefill throughput but increase activation memory. Decode-heavy workloads usually need smaller values.\n"
"4. Tune `--max-num-seqs` according to service concurrency. Requests above this value wait in the queue and the waiting time is counted in TTFT and TPOT.\n"
"5. Tune `--gpu-memory-utilization`. Increase it to provide more KV cache, but leave headroom for runtime memory fluctuation and expert imbalance.\n"
"6. Tune ACLGraph capture. `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` is recommended for decode. If you set `cudagraph_capture_sizes` manually, include common decode batch sizes. With FlashComm1, use capture sizes that are multiples of TP size."
msgstr ""

msgid "### 9.3 Model-Specific Optimizations"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"| Optimization | Enablement | Benefit | Notes |\n"
"| ------------ | ---------- | ------- | ----- |\n"
"| Hybrid attention support | Enabled by model implementation | Supports Qwen3.6 long-context inference. | Tune context length based on KV cache capacity. |\n"
"| Full decode ACLGraph | `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` | Reduces operator dispatch overhead and stabilizes decode performance. | Recommended for decode-heavy serving. |\n"
"| FlashComm1 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_flashcomm1\": true}'` | Reduces communication overhead in TP and high-concurrency scenarios. | May not help low-concurrency workloads. |\n"
"| Shared expert overlap | `--additional-config '{\"multistream_overlap_shared_expert\": true}'` | Overlaps shared expert computation in MoE workloads. | Recommended for throughput scenarios. |\n"
"| Asynchronous scheduling | `--async-scheduling` | Improves high-concurrency throughput by using non-blocking scheduling. | Disable it and compare if the workload is latency-sensitive. |\n"
"| Prefix caching | `--enable-prefix-caching` | Improves repeated-prefix workloads. | Monitor HBM usage for long-context workloads. |\n"
"| Qwen3.6 MTP speculative decoding | `--speculative-config '{\"method\": \"qwen3_5_mtp\", \"num_speculative_tokens\": 3, \"enforce_eager\": true}'` | Can improve decode throughput when stable and accepted tokens are high. | Validate stability, TTFT, TPOT, and throughput for your workload. |"
msgstr ""

